1
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:22,200
Are you sure they are here?

2
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:24,800
Last night, my sister drank with Lord Fang

3
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,960
and didn't come home all night.

4
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:26,800
I...

5
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,840
Sister!

6
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,320
Lord Fang!

7
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,600
Come out!

8
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,120
Ruilang.

9
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,169
What are you fussing about now?

10
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,780
My father trusted you so much,

11
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,260
recommending you as the Imperial Envoy,

12
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,920
sending you here to investigate and share the Emperor's burden.

13
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:21,780
But look at you.

14
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,760
Your head is full of romance and scandal.

15
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,220
How can you face my father?

16
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,320
Ruilang,

17
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,380
what nonsense are you talking about?

18
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,680
Let me ask you.

19
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:37,280
Did you get Miss Gu drunk last night on purpose

20
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,840
to do those dirty things?

21
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,800
You can insult me,

22
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,820
but you cannot slander Miss Gu's innocence.

23
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,520
Why are you...

24
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,200
Who bullied you?

25
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,860
I'll go fight them for you.

26
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,920
No.

27
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,360
No one bullied me.

28
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,280
It's my fault.

29
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:24,079
Sister, you didn't come back last night.

30
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,970
I was so afraid something happened to you.

31
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,000
What could happen to me?

32
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:31,560
I just drank too much last night.

33
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,560
Look, I'm perfectly fine.

34
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,760
You are fine,

35
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,720
but it's my fault.

36
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,160
I was wrong.

37
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,079
Don't be sad.

38
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,360
I'll listen to you from now on, Yan'er.

39
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,160
I won't drink so much ever again.

40
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,560
Sister,

41
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:49,240
you stop me from getting close to Lord Fang at every turn.

42
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,520
Are you eyeing this good match for yourself?

43
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,320
No way.

44
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,450
Who would want to marry him?

45
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,200
But I think Lord Fang is quite nice.

46
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,800
He is upright,

47
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,580
and handsome and dashing.

48
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,680
He's not that great.

49
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,970
Relying on being a royal relative,

50
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,800
he always has a sour face,

51
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,480
and he's so pretentious.

52
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,610
He speaks all fancy,

53
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:14,520
and cares about his looks more than a girl.

54
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,560
Dressing like a flashy butterfly every day.

55
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,320
Not a hair out of place,

56
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:20,519
and not a single wrinkle on his clothes.

57
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,520
Lord Fang.

58
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,000
Lord Fang.

59
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,120
You did that on purpose.

60
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,040
Have you seen the Little Marquis?

61
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,920
I've looked everywhere but can't find him.

62
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,000
Haven't seen him.

63
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,520
I'll go look again.

64
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,920
Have you seen Fang Ji?

65
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,520
I saw him just now.

66
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,800
But now...

67
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,040
I don't know.

68
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,000
You're useless.

69
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:07,880
Did you fight?

70
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,160
None of your business.

71
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,010
What's his problem?

72
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,360
Brother Fang.

73
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,200
Brother Jian.

74
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,520
Chancellor Fang's boat has arrived at Wangjiadu Ferry.

75
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:41,760
The Governor is throwing a banquet to welcome him.

76
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:45,400
Please come with us to the banquet, Brother Fang.

77
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,000
What is my father doing here?

78
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,280
Since you solved the case,

79
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:54,720
the Emperor allowed your father to visit you.

80
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,320
I have official business to attend to.

81
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,200
If he is fine,

82
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,080
tell him to return to the capital as soon as possible.

83
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:01,880
Brother Fang,

84
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,840
you really are putting me on the spot.

85
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:06,500
As if I haven't offended enough people already.

86
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,000
Then I will see him tomorrow.

87
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:13,360
Brother Jian, please give my regards to my father.

88
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,640
Brother Fang.

89
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,160
Fang Ji?

90
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,120
What's wrong?

91
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,760
What happened to Fang Ji?

92
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,600
Wha...

93
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,300
Is the investigation not going well?

94
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,480
It has been ascertained that

95
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,960
Xiong Renlian embezzled from the stores.

96
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:39,400
He conspired with the medium's wife and Min Huishi to use witchcraft.

97
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,880
They pretended to be ghosts

98
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,960
to steal official salt

99
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,020
for personal gain.

100
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,400
Furthermore,

101
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:47,450
many officials of various ranks are implicated.

102
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,960
Now,

103
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:51,680
except for those who are dead,

104
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,860
all the suspects have been arrested.

105
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,080
That's great.

106
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:59,880
This case is finally coming to an end.

107
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:03,280
Brother Fang can return to report on his mission.

108
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:06,200
But why did they send Huang Wansan and the others

109
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,860
to wreak havoc in the capital?

110
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,340
That remains unclear.

111
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,840
There may be a greater conspiracy behind it.

112
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,730
No, we can't investigate any further.

113
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,600
If we continue,

114
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,400
more people will be implicated.

115
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:23,200
Listen to me, Miss Gu.

116
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:27,370
Lu Shen, the Governor-General of Shuoyuan, is deeply entrenched.

117
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:27,960
He is duplicitous

118
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:28,920
and ruthless.

119
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,320
If you offend him,

120
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:33,000
the consequences will be unthinkable.

121
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:36,560
I'm afraid I already have.

122
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:37,880
What do you mean?

123
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,120
It's getting late.

124
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,760
Lord Jian, let's talk later.

125
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,560
Safe travels.

126
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:43,760
Miss.

127
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,500
What are you doing?

128
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,120
I heard Lord Fang hit the Young Marquis.

129
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:02,880
Who?

130
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,200
Who hit whom?

131
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,360
The Young Marquis thought you were being bullied,

132
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,160
so he went to confront Lord Fang.

133
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:10,280
But Lord Fang slapped him.

134
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:15,080
For someone like Fang Ji to get physical,

135
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:19,320
the Young Marquis must have said something completely out of line.

136
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:21,380
He was just trying to stand up for you.

137
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,000
Stand up for me?

138
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,360
What is there for him to stand up for?

139
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:29,360
Why do I get the feeling you're biased toward Lord Fang?

140
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,520
I'm just looking at the facts.

141
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,520
Let me, let me.

142
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,000
Young Marquis.

143
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,240
Young Marquis.

144
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,330
What are you doing here?

145
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,480
If you're on his side, leave now.

146
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,520
What do you mean, whose side?

147
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,600
I came specifically to see you.

148
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,360
See me?

149
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,600
What for?

150
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:18,960
I heard Fang Ji really crossed the line.

151
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,040
How could he hit someone?

152
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,360
He's way too impulsive.

153
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,080
What kind of person is he?

154
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,240
Don't you agree, Pihu?

155
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,160
Exactly.

156
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,400
Our Young Marquis is so precious.

157
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,600
Usually, if he loses even a single hair,

158
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,480
the Imperial Preceptor feels heartbroken.

159
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:34,360
Besides, Lord Fang is strange, too.

160
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:36,520
They were actually close as children.

161
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,000
When the Young Marquis wet the bed and wouldn't admit it,

162
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,800
Lord Fang took the punishment for him.

163
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:40,160
Really?

164
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:40,620
Really.

165
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:42,720
Enough.

166
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:52,760
Let me ask you,

167
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,520
do you like him?

168
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,360
Like what about him?

169
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,760
That he never looks people in the eye when he speaks?

170
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:04,560
Or that he's impulsive and likes to hit people?

171
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:08,180
Of course, he does have some good points.

172
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,160
For example,

173
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,400
he is upright.

174
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,560
I'm asking you,

175
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,000
do you like him?

176
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:16,960
Sister,

177
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:21,080
the Prime Minister wants to see you.

178
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:26,320
You've got some nerve.

179
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:30,080
Using the investigation as an excuse for leisure,

180
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:32,600
and bringing a woman along.

181
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,800
She's a femme fatale.

182
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,600
I heard you even hit your cousin for her.

183
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:41,560
You truly are a "good" son.

184
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:45,600
Father, it's not what you think.

185
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,960
Enough.

186
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,880
I don't want to hear your excuses.

187
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:53,940
His Majesty originally acknowledged your success in the case

188
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,000
and sent me to commend you.

189
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,080
But now it seems

190
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,280
it was nothing but dumb luck.

191
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,560
You are still so obstinate.

192
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:06,160
You haven't improved at all in all these years.

193
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:09,720
Fine.

194
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,200
When I return to the capital,

195
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,600
I will report to His Majesty

196
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,600
to appoint another imperial envoy,

197
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,080
so the case won't be jeopardized.

198
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,160
This matter is of grave importance.

199
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,160
It is no trifling matter.

200
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:20,160
Precisely because it is important,

201
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,600
a suitable candidate must be appointed.

202
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:26,600
Otherwise, how can our Fang family answer to His Majesty?

203
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,930
If you didn't have an Imperial Preceptor for an uncle

204
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:33,160
and a Prime Minister for a father,

205
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,320
do you think...

206
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,280
someone like you,

207
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,800
with your abilities,

208
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,000
could be the Right Censor-in-Chief?

209
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,480
Everything I have today

210
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,960
was earned through my own hard work.

211
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,520
I didn't rely on anyone's charity,

212
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:47,420
and I have a clear conscience.

213
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,160
Prime Minister,

214
00:11:56,960 --> 00:12:00,480
if you truly care about the imperial court,

215
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:04,000
please handle this impartially

216
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,020
and do not listen only to one side.

217
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,600
You ungrateful brat.

218
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,800
If you ruin this case,

219
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,050
I will hold you fully responsible.

220
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,360
Mother.

221
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:51,480
I saw Father today.

222
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:53,880
We argued again.

223
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,480
I miss you.

224
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,520
I will find the evidence soon

225
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:04,000
and avenge you.

226
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,360
What is it?

227
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:42,200
Why aren't you with your Official Fang today?

228
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,080
What do you want with me?

229
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,200
I'm still angry.

230
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,800
If you keep sounding so jealous,

231
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:48,530
I'm going to get the wrong idea.

232
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,800
Just kidding.

233
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:55,520
How could the Little Marquis fall for me?

234
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:56,770
Why couldn't...

235
00:13:57,720 --> 00:14:00,240
I actually need your help, Little Marquis.

236
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:03,080
And you're the only one who can do it.

237
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,320
Really?

238
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,520
Tell me.

239
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:17,320
A glance at the mist, a fleeting dream.

240
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:24,200
Moonlight singing alone to the breeze.

241
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:28,120
Persistence blooms in the silent night.

242
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:31,840
Promises made in youth.

243
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,720
For love,

244
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:37,560
A profound page is written.

245
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:41,120
A melody, a pot of wine.

246
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:44,600
A melody, a pot of wine.
